', 'modified': '2020-08-02T18:49:20Z'}

{'id': 36285568, 'body': 'Thank you for taking the time to try Breeze and providing your feedback on our personality and career tests. We're genuinely sorry to hear that your experience with the tests was not satisfactory.

We appreciate your feedback on the options available in the personality test and agree that including an "unsure" or "can't decide" option could be beneficial.

We take your feedback seriously and will work to improve our tests based on your suggestions. If you have any further concerns or questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to us at support@basenjiapps.com. ', 'modified': '2023-05-02T14:13:05Z'}

{'id': 30046173, 'body': "Thank you for sharing your thoughts with us!

As for the price, we understand its importance. If you like key functionality that's available for free, don't hesitate to contact us at support@basenjiapps.com to learn about our special offers and promotions.

As for the tests you've seen in ads, these are the features we'd love to add in our future updates. Tests and courses are Breeze premium features that require a subscription. Now, you can take the first test for free and access others after you buy a subscription.", 'modified': '2022-05-30T10:08:11Z'}

{'id': 35953135, 'body': "Thank you for sharing your experience with our app. We appreciate your feedback, and we're sorry to hear that our premium features didn't meet your expectations. We understand that the cost of our app can be a barrier for some of our users, and we want to assure you that we're committed to creating an app that is accessible to everyone who needs it.

We'd like to let you know that we offer a range of free features, including mood journaling, goal tracking, and basic statistics on your progress. While we understand that these features may not provide the same level of insight as our premium tests, they can still be useful in gaining a better understanding of yourself and your goals.

We also understand that your parents may not allow you to participate in free trials, and we're sorry to hear that this prevented you from using our app as intended. We'd like to assure you that we're always looking for ways to improve our app and make it more accessible to all of our users. We appreciate your feedback and will take it into consideration as we continue to evolve our app.", 'modified': '2023-04-14T09:12:24Z'}

{'id': 39077759, 'body': "We're genuinely sorry for the frustration you've experienced, and we appreciate your feedback. It's essential to us that our users have a clear and positive experience with our app.

Regarding the test and subscription, we apologize for any confusion. To assist you with your subscription cancellation, please reach out to our support team directly at support@bsnj.co. They can guide you through the process and address your concerns.
Your satisfaction and peace of mind are important to us, and we'll work to make this right for you.", 'modified': '2023-09-22T12:38:39Z'}

{'id': 39076898, 'body': "Thank you for your feedback regarding our introductory test. We appreciate your input, and we're sorry to hear that you had a frustrating experience with it.

Our goal with the introductory test is to configure the app according to your answers to provide tailored recommendations and support. We understand that the accuracy of these recommendations is crucial. Your feedback regarding the questions and answer choices is valuable, and we'll review and improve the test to ensure it provides more accurate and practical recommendations.

We're committed to making our app a valuable resource for your mental health journey, and your input helps us achieve that goal. If you have any further suggestions or concerns, please don't hesitate to reach out.", 'modified': '2023-09-22T11:47:46Z'}

{'id': 31712502, 'body': "Thank you for your feedback! We're sorry to hear that you find a gender test offensive. In our app, you can find only well-known tests, and this gender test is a Bem Sex-Role Inventory (BSRI). It was created by Sandra Bem to measure androgyny and published in 1974, so it may sound a bit conservative today.

As for inputting your feelings and tasks, we ask you to do it to give you precise stats to help you minimize stress factors and increase calm and happiness in your life.

Always feel free to share your thoughts with us! You can contact us at support@basenjiapps.com ‚Äî we'll be glad to receive an email from you!", 'modified': '2022-08-29T08:08:04Z'}

{'id': 22680679, 'body': "Thank you for telling us about your experience!

 Let us comment on our pricing structure. The key Breeze features are available for free and include journaling your mood, tracking what influenced it, seeing basic stats on your days, and accessing the first course and test. A paid subscription allows key functionality to stay free and allows you to access premium content to elevate your experience.

We are very happy to hear about your progress in struggling with anxeity. We do believe in you, please be strong and happy! We're here for you when you need us. ‚ù§Ô∏è", 'modified': '2021-05-07T14:05:24Z'}

